'''= Independent thinker and writer on environmental issues, author of [[Lean Logic]]'''

==Bio==
Born 1940, died 2010.
He was a significant figure in the development of the UK Green Party,<ref>[http://archive.greenparty.org.uk/information/silvergreen.htm Green Party Archives]</ref> the [[Transition Town Movement]],<ref>[http://www.theecologist.org/blogs_and_comments/commentators/other_comments/700941/dr_david_fleming_a_tribute.html David Fleming obituary in ''The Ecologist'']</ref> and the [[New Economics Foundation]].<ref>[http://www.neweconomics.org/blog/2010/12/01/david-fleming-1940-2010 David Fleming obituary from the New Economics Foundation, by David Boyle]</ref> (from Wikipedia)

